            h1 Aron Szanto - Founder and CEO
            p.lead.lh-180(style="font-size:20px;")

              | Aron leads the Zerobase Foundation team. Aron’s background is in the study of the spread of misinformation through social networks. He holds dual research and engineering appointments at Harvard University and Kensho Technologies, where his work lies at the intersection of machine learning on networks and natural language processing. He was formerly Product Engineering Manager at MarketFactory and has published research in the areas of machine learning, privacy and security, and high-performance data systems. Aron completed undergraduate and graduate study in applied mathematics at Harvard University.

